## COMPOSE

bind attach <return> view-mailcap
# bind attach l view-mailcap

### Markdown

# macro compose Y "<filter-entry>~/bin/mutt_markdown.py<enter>" "Convert markdown to multipart/alternative"
# macro compose M "<filter-entry>~/bin/mutt_markdown.py<enter>" "Convert markdown to multipart/alternative"
# macro compose Y "<pipe-entry>cat > TMP<Enter>"
macro compose Y "<pipe-entry>~/bin/mutt_markdown.sh<Enter>\
<attach-file>/tmp/email.txt<Enter>\
<tag-entry>\
<toggle-disposition>\
<attach-file>/tmp/juice.html<Enter>\
<tag-entry>\
<toggle-disposition>\
<view-attach>\
<attach-file>/tmp/email.md<Enter>\
<tag-entry>\
<toggle-disposition>\
<edit-type><home><kill-line>text/markdown; charset=utf-8<enter>\
<group-alternatives>" "Convert Markdown to HTML/Plain Multipart"


## SIDEBAR
bind index,pager \Ck sidebar-prev
bind index,pager \Cj sidebar-next
bind index,pager \Co sidebar-open
bind index,pager \Cp sidebar-prev-new
bind index,pager \Cn sidebar-next-new
bind index,pager B sidebar-toggle-visible


## LINE EDITOR (To: Bindings)
bind editor <space> noop
bind editor <Tab> complete-query
bind editor ^T complete


## IMAP

bind pager ,u imap-fetch-mail
